I got a coupon for a free 11" pizza from [Dewey’s Pizza](http://deweyspizza.com/) at the [Emerald City Half and Quarter Marathon](/blog/emerald-city-quarter-marathon.html) this year.
I hadn't been to Dewey's since it had first opened in Columbus several years ago.

I did some research and to my surprise the crust (for both the pizza and calzones) and the red sauce were both vegan!

