Overall our pizza seemed a little light on sauce and if I went back I'd definitely ask for extra sauce.
On top of that the vegtables weren't super fresh and some were clearly from a can.
Despite that it was pretty tasty!
We ate until stuffed and polished off the rest the next morning.
